In the Matter of Agustin Alamo, Appellant, v George M. Spanakos et al., Respondents, and Democratic County Committee of Bronx County et al., Respondents.

[— NYS2d —]

Judgment, Supreme Court, Bronx County (John P. Collins, J.), entered on February 9, 1994, unanimously affirmed, with*342out costs and without disbursements. No opinion. Concur — Rosenberger, J. P., Kupferman, Nardelli, Williams and Tom, JJ.
